Loading screen:

to fire loading screen:
                    Swal.fire({
                        title: 'Please Wait !',
                        html: 'Data Executing', // add html attribute if you want or remove
                        allowOutsideClick: false,
                        onBeforeOpen: () => {
                            Swal.showLoading()
                        },
                        onAfterClose() {
                            Swal.hideLoading()
                        },
                    });
                    
                    
                    to stop Swal:
                    Swal.stop();
